                           <locus target="#00" n="#"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 1v: [እ]ሴብህ፡ ጸጋኪ፡…</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 1v: I praise Your grace...</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 2r: Rejoice, Mary...</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 2v: ኩሎሙ፡ ሠራዊተ፡ መላእክት፡ መንፈሳውያን፡…</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 2v: All hosts of the spiritual angels…</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The word ድንግል፡ (“Virgin”) is written (in black ink, by the scribe) in the upper margin of fol. 47v; the word በከመ፡ (“Like, as”) is written upside down (in black ink, by the scribe) in the bottom margin of fol. 48v.&#xD;
- Several names are written in red ink in the same hand as the main text on fol. 56r, at the end of the text: [ወለ]ተ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ [ገብ]ረ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ወልደ፡ ማርያም።, [Wälä]ttä Täklä  Haymanot, [G]äbrä Täklä Haymanot, Wäldä Maryam.&#xD;
- A note mentioning the title ውእቱ፡ ሰአታት፡ ዘቤተ፡ ክርስትያን፡ “This is the Hours of the church”, and a personal name in Latin script, Kahsay, are written (recently; in pencil) on fol. 57r.&#xD;
- The title of the work (ሠአታት) is written in pen in the upper margin of fol. 1r.&#xD;
- A simple black line is used as text divider on fols. 50v and 56r.&#xD;
- Corrections (words or letters) are written interlineally and in the margins: fols. 14v, 54v.&#xD;
- Immediate corrections indicated by thin lines above and below the word: fols. 5r, 48r.&#xD;
- Erasures: fols. 8r, 10r.&#xD;
- Crude minor notes: fols. 1r, 19v, 20v, 22r, 23r, 25v, 26r, 29r, 30v, 33v, 34r, 57v.&#xD;
- Crude drawing on fol. 1r.</item>
                     </list>
